# -*-perl-*-

=head1 NAME

REDUCE_DREAMSTARE_QL - Process DREAM/STARE images

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Basic processing recipe suitable for DREAM/STARE images with the
quick-look pipeline.

=head1 KNOWN ISSUES

This primitive can not handle time series observing modes.

=head1 AUTHOR

Andy Gibb E<lt>agg@astro.ubc.caE<gt>,
